              ></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- FAQ Item -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow p-4">
            <button
              class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center
                           text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-medium
                           hover:text-yellow-600 dark:hover:text-yellow-400
                           transition-colors"
              data-accordion-button
            >
              What do I have to do?
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div
              class="mt-2 hidden text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              data-accordion-content
            >
              All you need to do is send us a few pictures or short videos of
              your machinery using your smartphone an iPhone works perfectly!
              That’s it. You don’t need to worry about professional equipment or
              perfect shots. We’ll take care of the rest, transforming your raw
              footage into high-quality, eye-catching content that attracts
              buyers and boosts your sales. Our goal is to make it as easy and
              hassle-free as possible for you!
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ Item -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow p-4">
            <button
              class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center
                           text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-medium
                           hover:text-yellow-600 dark:hover:text-yellow-400
                           transition-colors"
              data-accordion-button
            >
              We’ve tried social media or online marketing before and saw
              minimal results. How is this different?
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div
              class="mt-2 hidden text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              data-accordion-content
            >
              We focus specifically on the heavy machinery sector, using
              tailored campaigns and data-driven strategies. Rather than generic
              ads, we create high-impact, solution-oriented content that
              resonates with serious buyers and renters, translating directly
              into quality leads.
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ Item -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow p-4">
            <button
              class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center
                           text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-medium
                           hover:text-yellow-600 dark:hover:text-yellow-400
                           transition-colors"
              data-accordion-button
            >
              We’re not tech-savvy and worry new systems will complicate our
              workflow.
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div
              class="mt-2 hidden text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              data-accordion-content
            >
              We integrate seamlessly with your existing tools and processes.
              From easy content uploads to straightforward reporting dashboards,
              we design every step to be user-friendly and require minimal time
              on your part.
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ Item -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow p-4">
            <button
              class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center
                           text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-medium
                           hover:text-yellow-600 dark:hover:text-yellow-400
                           transition-colors"
              data-accordion-button
            >
              I’m worried about hidden fees or long-term contracts.
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div
              class="mt-2 hidden text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              data-accordion-content
            >
              We believe in complete transparency and a results-driven
              approach—no hidden fees, no retainers, and no surprise add-ons.
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ Item -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow p-4">
            <button
              class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center
                           text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-medium
                           hover:text-yellow-600 dark:hover:text-yellow-400
                           transition-colors"
              data-accordion-button
            >
              Our audience comes through word of mouth and trade shows, not
              social media. How can online marketing help?
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div
              class="mt-2 hidden text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              data-accordion-content
            >
              Even if your strongest leads come from referrals and expos,
              chances are they research online before making a final decision. A
              robust digital presence ensures you’re top-of-mind when they’re
              ready to buy or rent, complementing traditional channels and
              expanding your reach.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>

  <!-- Bottom bar with copyright -->
  <div class="b mt-8 py-2">
    <Container
      className="flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
    >
      <div>
        &copy; <span id="year"></span> Resloup. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </Container>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  // Simple accordion toggle
  document.querySelectorAll("[data-accordion-button]").forEach((button) => {
    button.addEventListener("click", () => {
      const content = button.nextElementSibling;
      content.classList.toggle("hidden");
      // Optional: rotate arrow icon
      const icon = button.querySelector("svg");
      icon.classList.toggle("rotate-180");
    });
  });

  // Current year
  document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>

<style>
  .logo {
    width: 10vw;
    min-width: 140px;
  }
  /* Smooth rotation transition for the FAQ icon */
  [data-accordion-button] svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
</style>
